<p>The UI on TextMate is nicer than BB Edit, but they both suck as editors. I like vim, not because of its nice interface (it also sucks) but because I&#8217;ve been using it for ten years. No other reason.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a target="_blank" title="http://lowmag.net" href="http://notabug.com/mt/gorsnikat.cgi?__mode=red;id=3046">Eli Sarver</a> at October 11, 2004 06:04 AM <a href="001434#c3046">#</a></p>

